---
title: Crispy Falafel Wraps with Hummus Slaw and Pickled Onions
description: These wraps come fully loaded with crispy falafel covered in sweet honey and a nutty, hummus-dressed slaw. The pickled red onions give a perfect acidic kick to liven up the palate!
